A vintage 1960s-style technical illustration showing two massive mechanical gears interlocking, one weathered and rust-colored representing legacy systems, the other sleek and chrome representing modern technology. Between the gears, streams of punch cards and magnetic tape ribbons flow and transform into glowing data streams. The scene is set against a muted olive and cream background with subtle halftone dot patterns. A retro mainframe computer console sits in the corner with spinning tape reels. The overall aesthetic evokes mid-century technical manuals and engineering diagrams, with warm sepia tones and deliberate grain texture suggesting aged paper.
